criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. aged ≤ 18 years;

          2. newly diagnosed as the four main categories of NHL(Burkitt's lymphoma, lymphoblastic
             lymphoma, anaplastic large cell lymphoma, and diffuse large B-cell lymphoma) between
             2014 and 2020;

          3. treated according to the modified BFM95 protocol.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. aged ＞ 18 years;

          2. not newly diagnosed as the four main categories of NHL between 2014 and 2020;

          3. treated according to chemotherapeutic regimens except for the modified BFM95 protocol.
